**What's happening:**
- [Profile.jsx:94-99](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Profile.jsx#L94-L99): Direct `supabase.from('profiles').select()` for username check
- [Profile.jsx:148-153](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Profile.jsx#L148-L153): Direct `supabase.storage.from('avatars').upload()`
